The roof top pool and lounge area with bar was our favorite place to meet for a drink and the views of the city at the end of the day.	The service was great and breakfast was ample, with the usual cereals, breads and cheeses etc.	The breakfast was a good selection of cereals, ham, cheese, eggs, fruit, yohgurt etc.	The terrace & pool on the roof was beautifull, a relaxing place to sit in the sun with nice cocktails.	The hotel has a small bar near the reception desk where you can get a coffee or drink at most times of the day and into the evenings.